<p><b>PolyGram</b> was the name of the <a href="Major_label" title="Major label" class="mw-redirect">major label</a> recording company started by <a href="Philips" title="Philips">Philips</a> as a <a href="Holding_company" title="Holding company">holding company</a> for its music interests in 1945. In 1999 it was sold to <a href="Seagram" title="Seagram">Seagram</a> and merged into <a href="Universal_Music_Group" title="Universal Music Group">Universal Music Group</a>.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc">
<tr>
<td>
